<section class="py-20 bg-primary-600">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class=" mx-auto text-center">
      <!-- Title -->
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        订阅 RSS，第一时间获取更新！
      </h2>
      
      <!-- Description -->
      <p class="text-primary-100 mb-8 text-lg">
        轻松接收最新文章，随时掌握一手资讯。点击订阅，不错过任何精彩内容！
      </p>
      
      <!-- Input and Button Group -->
      <div class="flex gap-4 max-w-md mx-auto">
        <input
          type="text"
          value="/rss.xml"
          readonly
          class="flex-1 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-transparent bg-white/20 text-white placeholder-primary-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/30 transition-all duration-300"
        />
        <button
          onclick="window.location.href='/rss.xml';"
          class="px-6 py-3 bg-white text-primary-600 font-medium rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-50 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/30"
        >
          立即订阅
        </button>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Footer Statement -->
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-primary-100">
        一键订阅，快速获取最新文章和动态，节省时间，提升效率！
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
